{"tid":2109780,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友同佢以前暗戀既人一齊做野","createTime":"2020-07-15T12:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T18:26:22.000Z","uid":244852,"like":12,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7468e1679c4b8cdc784acbb35af953c3c1e99339","tid":2109780,"uid":244852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:34:20.000Z","msg":"(文長注意)<br />\n我同男朋友拍左啱啱好2年拖<br />\n佢識我之前一直鐘意佢個同事(叫阿A)<br />\n但阿A當時有男朋友 加上佢地年齡差 所有人都話佢地冇可能<br />\n我男朋友之後都放棄左佢（聲稱）<br />\n而阿A一直唔知道我男朋友暗戀佢<br />\n<br />\n之後我個fd係佢地間公司做 就介紹左我比我男朋友識<br />\n佢地所有同事都覺得我好似阿A 無論身高 外表 性格<br />\n連我都覺我地好似...<br />\n之後我同男朋友就一齊左<br />\n作為A0既小毒毒 其實我一開始都覺得男朋友係咪因為我似阿A所以先鐘意我 但佢一直都死口話唔係 <br />\n<br />\n之後每次講親A佢都會好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢都好錫我 我就一直冇理到<br />\n但奇怪既係 我同A見面時 男朋友會親口話我地好似<br />\n<br />\n但我最近發現<br />\n1. 阿A個wts通知成日彈岀黎 佢地好似成日whatsapp<br />\n我同男朋友講番我唔鍾意 講完之後好似真係少見左阿A既whatsapp通知 (但唔知會唔會係mute/hide左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n2. 講親A 佢開口埋口都讚A靚 會話我醜樣 <br />\n3. 因為佢地係同事 佢地會單獨食飯<br />\n (而呢樣野係我fd話番比我聽 佢唔會報備)<br />\n<br />\n4. 我fd有時講起佢地公司野 會發現男朋友成日幫住A做野/講好說話<br />\n5. 會係IG寫有關於A既野(拍拖前) 但從來唔會岀現有關我既post <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我知道佢地應該冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而A係未結婚 唔知佢宜家有冇男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw不推文 thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大方d 同男朋友傾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁介意分手啦"},{"pid":"0489b973931697787f1ebef99061a061211e69fd","tid":2109780,"uid":208285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:43:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"limegreen\">帽</span>事既"},{"pid":"581ee1a5bfd1b1804cd6efbec524480b6c94512c","tid":2109780,"uid":343268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d81809867ae91095720a36bea4850baa87fbaad","tid":2109780,"uid":244852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0489b973931697787f1ebef99061a061211e69fd","tid":2109780,"uid":208285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:43:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"limegreen\">帽</span>事既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406f3583c1af81c1690dc3ad65753e1fc7bb4269","tid":2109780,"uid":199330,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"分手啦後備嚟嘅咋你水泡嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你未去到咁差嘅 但係有人送上門點解唔要啊"},{"pid":"78c4330af2691a952a204d0a93f664ff375df712","tid":2109780,"uid":244852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"406f3583c1af81c1690dc3ad65753e1fc7bb4269","tid":2109780,"uid":199330,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"分手啦後備嚟嘅咋你水泡嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你未去到咁差嘅 但係有人送上門點解唔要啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"巴打你講得好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身都覺得佢宜家鐘意/錫我就得 但夜晚諗男朋友鐘意既可能唔係我 就成日夜晚自己喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf98c8962f071ce967a1e5f49b796bd27791fc23","tid":2109780,"uid":222524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:07:31.000Z","msg":"你男友係咩類型男人先<br />\n大男人，有霸氣，好惡，友善，內向，外向，文靜，大方，小氣<br />\n<br />\n唔同類型男人，好影響佢會唔會肯同你傾<br />\n<br />\n不過都建議傾下先既<br />\n<br />\n或者可以用「我有個fd有咁既情況」睇下佢有咩反應"},{"pid":"806d32fc2aa3b8b8c7a9c26affe041297b8b5aef","tid":2109780,"uid":199330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78c4330af2691a952a204d0a93f664ff375df712","tid":2109780,"uid":244852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"406f3583c1af81c1690dc3ad65753e1fc7bb4269","tid":2109780,"uid":1993